parameters.query:
INSERT INTO Events (
    event_code, 
    event_name, 
    start_date, 
    stop_date, 
    location_id,
    event_type
) VALUES (
    $1,
    $2,
    $3::timestamp,
    $4::timestamp,
    '11440',
    'STERN_LEAGUE'
)
ON CONFLICT (event_code) 
DO UPDATE SET
    event_name = EXCLUDED.event_name,
    start_date = EXCLUDED.start_date,
    stop_date = EXCLUDED.stop_date,
    is_active = true;

-- Upsert Player
INSERT INTO Players (
    player_id, 
    display_name, 
    avatar_url,
    background_color_hex, 
    is_all_access,
    last_seen
) VALUES (
    $1,
    $2,
    $3,
    $4,
    $5::boolean,
    NOW()
)
ON CONFLICT (player_id) 
DO UPDATE SET
    display_name = EXCLUDED.display_name,
    avatar_url = EXCLUDED.avatar_url,
    background_color_hex = EXCLUDED.background_color_hex,
    is_all_access = EXCLUDED.is_all_access,
    last_seen = NOW();

-- Upsert Machine
INSERT INTO Machines (
    machine_id,
    machine_name,
    is_active
) VALUES (
    $6,
    $7,
    true
) 
ON CONFLICT (machine_id) 
DO UPDATE SET
    machine_name = EXCLUDED.machine_name,
    is_active = true;

-- Check if this score already exists or is lower than existing
SELECT 
    CASE 
        WHEN MAX(high_score) IS NULL THEN true
        WHEN MAX(high_score) < $3 THEN true
        ELSE false
    END as should_insert,
    $1 as player_id,
    $2 as machine_id,
    $3 as high_score,
    $4 as date_set,
    $5 as event_code,
    $6 as score_source,
    $7 as is_approved
FROM High_Scores_Archive
WHERE player_id = $1
    AND machine_id = $2
    AND event_code = $5;
